Added a tracked `hooks/pre-push` hook because this repo already uses `core.hooksPath=hooks/`, so adding the file installs the scan for all local worktrees.

Reasoning: pre-commit is useful, but notes can still enter history via other paths. A pre-push `gitleaks git` scan gives a last line of defense that includes refs/notes/*.
